# {{PROJECT_NAME}} — PHIPA Breach Response Runbook

> **This is a starting-point template, not legal advice.** PHIPA breach
> obligations differ for HICs vs. Agents. If {{PROJECT_NAME}} is acting as
> an Agent on behalf of a HIC, the HIC has the primary statutory
> obligation and must be looped in immediately — your team supports
> notifications rather than driving them. Counsel involvement is
> expected from the moment a PHI breach is suspected.

